         <abstract id="aspace_221d9462ab4316abc0957f82069edcb3">The records consist of correspondence, memoranda, and reports documenting the activities and operations of the Yale University Alumni Board. Topics include alumni fund convocations, football games, cocktail parties, reunions, and finances.</abstract>
